==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Soundless
<hw>Sound"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not capable of
being sounded or fathomed; unfathomable.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Soundless</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Soundless
<hw>Sound"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no sound; noiseless;
silent.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Sound"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Sound"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Soundly</ent>⟦br⟧
